product.name: e.l.f. Intense Ink Eyeliner
product.description: e.l.f. Intense Ink Eyeliner quick-dry formula instantly enhances the lash line with rich and long-lasting colour. The felt tip pen allows you to create a sleek or bold line with complete precision. It glides on smoothly without smudging, feathering, or running! How To Use: Apply colour as close to the lash line as possible. For a thin line, use just the point of the pen tip, or slant the pen along the side for a thicker, bolder line Ingredients: Water (Aqua), Styrene/Acrylates/Ammonium Methacrylate Copolymer, Polysorbate 20, Ethyheyl Palmitate, PEG-40 Hydrogenated Castor Oil, Xanthan Gum, Benzyl Alcohol, Methylchloroisothiazolinone. MAY CONTAIN: DC Black #2 (CI 77266).
